-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingErrorKey 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingErrorKey

iOS 7.0+iPadOS 7.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.9+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemDownloadingErrorKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitemdownloadingerrorkey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSError`](/documentation/foundation/nserror) object that describes the problem that occurred when downloading the item from iCloud failed.
